nodes.text: Star Wars: Return of the Jedi Notebook Collection

The Star Wars: Return of the Jedi Notebook Collection is a set of three lined notebooks with cover artwork and spot quotations from the film Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi. It was published by Chronicle Books on April 24, 2018, as the follow-up to the Star Wars: A New Hope Notebook Collection and Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back Notebook Collection.
